13
00:00:34,719 --> 00:00:37,359
Every treatment failed, nothing worked.

14
00:00:37,359 --> 00:00:40,399
And instead of praying, I just sobbed.

15
00:00:40,399 --> 00:00:42,560
I couldn't stop. I didn't know how to.

16
00:00:43,840 --> 00:00:47,600
I sat in that hospital room, barely breathing from the grief.

17
00:00:48,640 --> 00:00:52,239
I thought if I cried hard enough, maybe things would change,

18
00:00:52,239 --> 00:00:55,039
but nothing changed until a friend showed up.

19
00:00:55,759 --> 00:00:57,759
He didn't try to explain the pain away.

20
00:00:58,719 --> 00:01:01,359
