21
00:01:02,240 --> 00:01:04,640
have you prayed? I hadn't.

22
00:01:05,519 --> 00:01:06,799
I didn't feel like I could.

23
00:01:07,439 --> 00:01:09,760
But that night, through the tears I did,

24
00:01:09,760 --> 00:01:11,519
I didn't pray for a miracle.

25
00:01:11,519 --> 00:01:13,680
