26
00:01:14,560 --> 00:01:19,359
And even though my dad didn't survive, that prayer, it still worked.

27
00:01:20,319 --> 00:01:23,039
It didn't save his body, but it saved my spirit.

28
00:01:24,000 --> 00:01:28,160
